You can simply ask Alexa to control your Isnow Smart Products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “Isnow Home” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “Isnow Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “Isnow Home” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the backlights.”
“Alexa, turn off the backlights.”
“Alexa, set the backlights to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the backlights to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the backlights to 50%.”
"Alexa, set backlights to green."
"Alexa, set backlights to cool white."
